{"tid":450804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙角邨倫常血案 老夫疑滙款至大陸親戚不果以菜刀斬傷妻","createTime":"2017-10-28T14:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T01:37:24.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b539f097b67fc37ade83daba405c9e7363eab5","tid":450804,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171028/57388015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F57388015&d=0Ai2mg3dltrynOGJmkIXk10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6de394e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F57388015&h=1cd3f2c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171028/57388015</a><br />\n<br />\n【21:33更新】事發時丈夫疑經銀行匯款給內地親戚，但遭妻子阻止，雙方起爭執釀血案<br />\n【19:21】女傷者情況穩定，其丈夫經治理後亦情況穩定，轉送那打素醫院。<br />\n【18:06】新增動新聞<br />\n<br />\n沙田沙角邨銀鷗樓發生傷人血案，下午1時39分，警方接報銀鷗樓一單位有人持刀斬人，破門入內發現兩名男女長者受傷。其中65歲女傷者頭部受傷血流如注，與其79歲丈夫先後送院，警現正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查顯示，兩人為夫婦關係，丈夫持長約30厘米的菜刀斬傷妻子。消息指，事發時丈夫疑經銀行匯款給內地親戚，但遭妻子阻止，雙方遂起爭執。警員接報到場，破門入屋時老翁並無反抗，將他拘捕及送院，警員同時在屋內撿獲涉案菜刀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n件事又係同大陸有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cb90a83be4086d8bc45b778ec282581118a6d0","tid":450804,"uid":53429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"70幾歲仲匯咩錢丫"},{"pid":"6fec3ada447ad46d39c52b68d2d877f547bac119","tid":450804,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:03:55.000Z","msg":"佢老婆係幫緊佢"},{"pid":"a6b1b4bd2185de7e97fc73005fd1bb4228af583c","tid":450804,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費醫療資源"},{"pid":"f260daf3ae4883194537946da3914fec0b44c89c","tid":450804,"uid":53126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"相差24歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de693bb1c660f59ba07941b855f133b28ec9d68","tid":450804,"uid":54056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相差24歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點計"},{"pid":"d72f24dc21bac042fe1edf7bcf295d2a0e091659","tid":450804,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"同支那相關<br />\n就算只係過數<br />\n都唔會有好下場"},{"pid":"64c119fcc18b747f4286af48290f9baefc53f320","tid":450804,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相差24歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}